HEADWORD: tortoise-shell
<hw>tortoise-shell</hw>, <pos>adj.</pos> <def>Having a color like that
of a tortoise's shell, black with white and orange spots; -- used mostly
to describe cats of that color.</def> <def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>a
tortoise-shell cat.</def></def2></p>

